         <entry xml:id="hognesin-ys"
            type="mainEntry"
            xml:lang="en"
            prev="#hognesin-dlgenr"
            next="#zeta-dlgenr"
            source="Yalkut Shimoni">
            <form type="lemma" opt="false">
               <orth type="lemma" xml:lang="jpa" opt="false" select="true">הוגנסין</orth>
               <orth type="transliteration" xml:lang="fjb" opt="false">hwgnsyn</orth>
               <pron notation="rabbinic" opt="false">hognesin</pron>
               <gramGrp opt="false">
                  <gram type="pos" opt="false">noun</gram>
                  <gram type="gen">m.</gram>
                  <gram type="num">pl.</gram>
               </gramGrp>
               <form type="variant" source="GenR 48,9 Vat1">
                  <orth type="variant" xml:lang="jpa">אבגניסים</orth>
                  <orth type="transliteration" xml:lang="fjb">ʾvgnysym</orth>
                  <pron notation="rabbinic">avgenisin</pron>
               </form>
               <form type="variant" source="GenR 48,9 Vat1">
                  <orth type="variant" xml:lang="jpa">אווגניסים</orth>
                  <orth type="transliteration" xml:lang="fjb">ʾwwgnysym</orth>
                  <pron notation="rabbinic">awgenisim</pron>
               </form>
            </form>
            <form type="inflected" opt="false">
               <orth type="inflected" xml:lang="jpa" opt="false">הוגניס*</orth>
               <orth type="transliteration" xml:lang="fjb" opt="false">hwgnys</orth>
               <pron notation="rabbinic" opt="false">hognis</pron>
               <gramGrp opt="false">
                  <gram type="num" opt="false">sg.</gram>
               </gramGrp>
            </form>
            <sense xml:id="hognesin-ys-1">
               <usg type="domain" opt="false">properties</usg>
               <usg type="socioCultural" norm="borrowing" opt="false">core borrowing</usg>
               <usg type="normativity" opt="false">standard</usg>
               <usg type="meaningType" opt="false">lit.</usg>
               <usg type="frequency" opt="false"/>
               <usg type="geographic" opt="false">Coptic <ref target="https://coptic-dictionary.org/entry.py?tla=C9062"
                  type="entry" targetLang="cop">ⲉⲩⲅⲉⲛⲏⲥ</ref></usg>
               <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en" subtype="sense">
                  <quote>noble, distinguished</quote>
               </cit>
               <cit type="translationEquivalent" xml:lang="grc">
                  <quote>εὐγενής</quote>
               </cit>
               <cit type="example" xml:lang="jpa">
                  <quote>
                     אמ' אם אני רואה שכינה ממתנת להם, אני יודע שהן בני אדם 
                     <app>
                        <lem>גדולים</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S V">הוגניסים</rdg>
                     </app>.
                     ואם רואה אני אותם שהם חולקין כבוד זה לזה, אני יודע שהן בני אדם 
                     <app>
                        <lem>הוגנסים</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S V">-</rdg>
                     </app>.
                     כיון שראה שחלקו כבוד זה לזה, ידע שהן 
                     <app>
                        <lem>הוגנסין</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S V">הוגניסים</rdg>
                     </app>.
                  </quote>
                  <bibl default="false" status="draft">
                     <ref type="witness">Yalq 82</ref>
                     <ref type="witness">I 352: 11;12</ref>
                  </bibl>
                  <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                     <quote>Said he [Abraham]: ‘If I see that the Shechinah waits to them, I will know that they are worthy; and if I see that they pay respect to each other, I will know that they are distinguished.’ And when he did see them pay respect to each other, he knew that they are distinguished. (Freedman / Simon 411)</quote>
                  </cit>
                  <note>= <bibl type="ancient">GenR 48,9 [II 486: 2,3]</bibl> (<term xml:lang="jpa">הוגנוסין</term>); <bibl type="ancient">LeqT 18,2 [41b]</bibl> (<term xml:lang="jpa">הוגנוסים</term>)</note>
               </cit>
            </sense>
            <ref type="bibliography">
               <bibl default="false" status="draft">
                  <title>Krauss, LW I</title>
                  <citedRange>223a</citedRange>
               </bibl>
            </ref>
